Put all local dependencies here. (if not already installed)

Dependencies:
==============

GLFWDisplay => glfw
OpenGLRenderer => glm

Note:
======

Mobile developpement requires OpenGL ES 2.0 or higher
Developpement for Linux, Mac OS or Windows requires OpenGL 3.0 or higher

Install:
=========

glfw:
- Link: http://sourceforge.net/projects/glfw/?source=dlp
- Extract it under glfw-2.7.7/
- Edit glfw-2.7.7/compile.sh and add the '-fPIC' option to GLFW_LIB_CFLAGS
- Compile it with "make x11"

glm:
- Link: http://sourceforge.net/projects/ogl-math/
- Extract glm/glm under glm/
